  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-physics-classical-mechanics-work-done-by-a-force> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''work done by a force''' ;
