<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-physics-classical-mechanics-conservation-of-mechanical-energy> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''conservation of mechanical energy''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''KE + U = constant (no non-conservative forces)''' ;
