<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-physics-electromagnetism-lorentz-force> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''Lorentz force''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''F = q*(E + v × B)''' ;
