<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-quantum-mechanics> skos:scopeNote '''wave functions and the Born rule; Schrödinger equation (time-dependent and time-independent); Dirac bra-ket notation and Hilbert space; operators, observables, and eigenvalue problems; uncertainty principle; quantum harmonic oscillator (ladder operators); angular momentum and spin; hydrogen atom and central potentials; identical particles: bosons and fermions; time-independent perturbation theory; time-dependent perturbation theory and Fermi's golden rule; variational principle and WKB approximation; scattering theory (Born approximation, partial waves)''' .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-quantum-mechanics-wave-function> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''wave function''' ;
