<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-quantum-mechanics-born-rule> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Born rule''' ;
  skos:definition '''The probability of measuring observable A and obtaining eigenvalue a_n is |<a_n|ψ>|^2; postulate connecting the mathematical formalism to experimental outcomes.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-quantum-mechanics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-quantum-mechanics-hilbert-space> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Hilbert space''' ;
  skos:definition '''The complete complex inner-product space of normalizable quantum states; observables are Hermitian operators on this space.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-quantum-mechanics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
