<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-physics-quantum-mechanics-canonical-commutation-relation> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''canonical commutation relation''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''[x̂_i, p̂_j] = iℏ*delta_ij''' ;
