<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-physics-quantum-mechanics-generalized-uncertainty-principle> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''generalized uncertainty principle''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''sigma_A * sigma_B >= (1/2)|<[Â,B̂]>|''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''theorem''' ;
