<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-physics-quantum-mechanics-harmonic-oscillator-energy-levels> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''harmonic oscillator energy levels''' ;
