<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-physics-quantum-mechanics-first-order-state-correction-perturbation-theory> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''first-order state correction (perturbation theory)''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''|n^(1)> = sum_{m≠n} <m^(0)|H'|n^(0)>/(E_n^(0)-E_m^(0)) * |m^(0)>''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''equation''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-quantum-mechanics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-physics-quantum-mechanics-fermi-s-golden-rule> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''Fermi's golden rule''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''Gamma_{i→f} = (2π/ℏ) * |<f|H'|i>|^2 * rho(E_f)''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''equation''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-quantum-mechanics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-physics-quantum-mechanics-born-approximation-scattering-amplitude> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''Born approximation (scattering amplitude)''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''f(θ) = -(m/(2πℏ^2)) * ∫ V(r') * exp(-i*q·r') d^3r'  where q = k_f - k_i''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''equation''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-quantum-mechanics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-physics-quantum-mechanics-optical-theorem> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''optical theorem''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''sigma_total = (4π/k) * Im[f(θ=0)]''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''theorem''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-quantum-mechanics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-statistical-mechanics-and-thermodynamics> a kcc:Topic ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Statistical Mechanics and Thermodynamics''' ;
  kcc:level '''graduate''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#domain-physics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-statistical-mechanics-and-thermodynamics> skos:scopeNote '''laws of thermodynamics; thermodynamic potentials (U, F, G, H) and Maxwell relations; microcanonical, canonical, and grand canonical ensembles; partition function and free energy; classical ideal gas and equipartition theorem; Fermi-Dirac and Bose-Einstein statistics; blackbody radiation and Planck distribution; phase transitions and critical phenomena; fluctuations and the fluctuation-dissipation theorem; entropy and the second law''' .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-statistical-mechanics-and-thermodynamics-entropy> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''entropy''' ;
  skos:definition '''A state function S = k_B * ln(Ω) (Boltzmann) or S = -k_B * sum(p_i * ln p_i) (Gibbs); quantifies the number of accessible microstates and the arrow of time.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-statistical-mechanics-and-thermodynamics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-statistical-mechanics-and-thermodynamics-partition-function> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''partition function''' ;
  skos:definition '''Z = sum_i exp(-β E_i) (canonical), where β = 1/(k_B T); the generating function for all thermodynamic quantities.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-statistical-mechanics-and-thermodynamics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-statistical-mechanics-and-thermodynamics-canonical-ensemble> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''canonical ensemble''' ;
  skos:definition '''Statistical description of a system in thermal contact with a heat reservoir at temperature T; probability of state i is p_i = exp(-β E_i)/Z.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-statistical-mechanics-and-thermodynamics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-statistical-mechanics-and-thermodynamics-grand-canonical-ensemble> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''grand canonical ensemble''' ;
  skos:definition '''Statistical description of a system exchanging both energy and particles with a reservoir; characterized by T and chemical potential μ.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-statistical-mechanics-and-thermodynamics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-statistical-mechanics-and-thermodynamics-grand-partition-function> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''grand partition function''' ;
  skos:definition '''Z_G = sum_{N,i} exp(-β(E_{N,i} - μN)) = sum_N z^N * Z_N, where z = exp(βμ) is the fugacity.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-statistical-mechanics-and-thermodynamics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-statistical-mechanics-and-thermodynamics-chemical-potential> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''chemical potential''' ;
  skos:definition '''μ = (∂F/∂N)_{T,V} = (∂G/∂N)_{T,P}; the free energy cost of adding one particle to the system at constant T and V (or P).''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-statistical-mechanics-and-thermodynamics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-statistical-mechanics-and-thermodynamics-equipartition-theorem> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''equipartition theorem''' ;
  skos:definition '''In classical statistical mechanics, each quadratic degree of freedom in the Hamiltonian contributes (1/2)k_B T to the mean energy.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-statistical-mechanics-and-thermodynamics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-statistical-mechanics-and-thermodynamics-fermi-dirac-distribution> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Fermi-Dirac distribution''' ;
  skos:definition '''The mean occupation number of a single-particle state with energy ε for identical fermions: f_FD(ε) = 1/(exp(β(ε-μ))+1).''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-statistical-mechanics-and-thermodynamics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-statistical-mechanics-and-thermodynamics-bose-einstein-distribution> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Bose-Einstein distribution''' ;
  skos:definition '''The mean occupation number of a single-particle state with energy ε for identical bosons: f_BE(ε) = 1/(exp(β(ε-μ))-1).''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-statistical-mechanics-and-thermodynamics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-statistical-mechanics-and-thermodynamics-fermi-energy> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Fermi energy''' ;
  skos:definition '''The chemical potential of an ideal Fermi gas at T = 0; the energy of the highest occupied state in the ground state.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-statistical-mechanics-and-thermodynamics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-statistical-mechanics-and-thermodynamics-bose-einstein-condensation> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Bose-Einstein condensation''' ;
  skos:definition '''The macroscopic occupation of the ground single-particle state below a critical temperature T_c in a gas of non-interacting bosons.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-statistical-mechanics-and-thermodynamics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-statistical-mechanics-and-thermodynamics-free-energy-helmholtz> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''free energy (Helmholtz)''' ;
  skos:definition '''F = U - TS; the thermodynamic potential minimized at equilibrium for a system at constant T and V; F = -k_B T * ln Z.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-statistical-mechanics-and-thermodynamics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-statistical-mechanics-and-thermodynamics-gibbs-free-energy> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Gibbs free energy''' ;
  skos:definition '''G = U + PV - TS = H - TS; the potential minimized at equilibrium for constant T and P; determines spontaneity of chemical/phase transitions.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-statistical-mechanics-and-thermodynamics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-statistical-mechanics-and-thermodynamics-fluctuation-dissipation-theorem> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''fluctuation-dissipation theorem''' ;
  skos:definition '''Relates spontaneous fluctuations of a system in equilibrium to its linear response (dissipation) to an external perturbation; e.g., Johnson-Nyquist noise in resistors.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-statistical-mechanics-and-thermodynamics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
