<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-condensed-matter-physics> a kcc:Topic ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Condensed Matter Physics''' ;
  kcc:level '''graduate''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#domain-physics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-condensed-matter-physics> skos:scopeNote '''crystal lattices: Bravais lattices and reciprocal lattice; Bloch's theorem and band structure; free electron model and density of states; nearly-free electron model and band gaps; tight-binding model; phonons and the Debye model; semiconductors: intrinsic, doped, p-n junctions; superconductivity: BCS theory and Meissner effect; magnetism: dia-, para-, ferro-, antiferromagnetism; mean-field theory and Landau theory of phase transitions''' .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-condensed-matter-physics-bravais-lattice> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Bravais lattice''' ;
  skos:definition '''A periodic array of points R = n_1 a_1 + n_2 a_2 + n_3 a_3 (n_i integers) that looks identical from every lattice point; there are 14 distinct Bravais lattices in 3D.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-condensed-matter-physics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-condensed-matter-physics-reciprocal-lattice> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''reciprocal lattice''' ;
  skos:definition '''The lattice of wave vectors G satisfying exp(iG·R) = 1 for all Bravais lattice vectors R; the natural space for diffraction and Bloch states.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-condensed-matter-physics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-condensed-matter-physics-brillouin-zone> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Brillouin zone''' ;
  skos:definition '''The Wigner-Seitz cell of the reciprocal lattice; the set of k-vectors closest to the origin; the irreducible domain for Bloch band structure.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-condensed-matter-physics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-condensed-matter-physics-bloch-s-theorem> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Bloch's theorem''' ;
  skos:definition '''The eigenstates of a Hamiltonian with lattice periodicity have the form ψ_{nk}(r) = u_{nk}(r)exp(ik·r) where u has the periodicity of the lattice.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-condensed-matter-physics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-condensed-matter-physics-band-gap> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''band gap''' ;
  skos:definition '''An energy range in which no electronic states exist in a crystalline solid; arises from Bragg scattering at Brillouin zone boundaries; determines semiconductor/insulator character.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-condensed-matter-physics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-condensed-matter-physics-effective-mass> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''effective mass''' ;
  skos:definition '''m* = ℏ^2 / (d^2E/dk^2); the curvature of the band dispersion; can be negative near band maxima (holes behave as positive-mass positive-charge carriers).''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-condensed-matter-physics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-condensed-matter-physics-phonon> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''phonon''' ;
  skos:definition '''A quantum of lattice vibration; a bosonic collective excitation with dispersion ω(k) governed by interatomic force constants; carries heat but not charge.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-condensed-matter-physics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-condensed-matter-physics-debye-model> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Debye model''' ;
  skos:definition '''Approximates the phonon density of states as ∝ ω^2 up to a cutoff ω_D; correctly gives C_V ~ T^3 at low temperature (Debye T^3 law).''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-condensed-matter-physics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-condensed-matter-physics-fermi-surface> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Fermi surface''' ;
  skos:definition '''The constant-energy surface in k-space at the Fermi energy; determines low-temperature electronic properties; topological changes drive Lifshitz transitions.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-condensed-matter-physics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-condensed-matter-physics-cooper-pair> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Cooper pair''' ;
  skos:definition '''A bound pair of electrons with opposite momenta and spins, stabilized by an attractive phonon-mediated interaction; the fundamental unit of the BCS superconducting condensate.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-condensed-matter-physics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-condensed-matter-physics-meissner-effect> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Meissner effect''' ;
  skos:definition '''The expulsion of magnetic flux from a superconductor below T_c; not merely perfect conductivity but active flux expulsion, confirming the thermodynamic nature of the superconducting state.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-condensed-matter-physics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-condensed-matter-physics-order-parameter> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''order parameter''' ;
  skos:definition '''A quantity (e.g., magnetization M, gap Δ in BCS, superfluid density) that is zero in the disordered phase and non-zero in the ordered phase; its symmetry and spatial variation classify the transition.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-condensed-matter-physics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-physics-condensed-matter-physics-bloch-theorem> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''Bloch theorem''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''psi_{nk}(r) = u_{nk}(r) * exp(i*k·r),  u_{nk}(r+R) = u_{nk}(r)''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''theorem''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-condensed-matter-physics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-physics-condensed-matter-physics-free-electron-dispersion> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''free electron dispersion''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''E(k) = ℏ^2*k^2 / (2m)''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''equation''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-condensed-matter-physics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-physics-condensed-matter-physics-density-of-states-3d-free-electron> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''density of states (3D free electron)''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''g(E) = (1/(2*pi^2)) * (2m/ℏ^2)^(3/2) * sqrt(E)''' ;
