<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-particle-physics-and-quantum-field-theory> skos:scopeNote '''natural units and particle properties; Standard Model: quarks, leptons, gauge bosons; Feynman diagrams and QED; gauge invariance and local symmetry; QCD and confinement/asymptotic freedom; electroweak unification and the Higgs mechanism; conservation laws: B, L, CP symmetry; Noether's theorem (field theory version); renormalization and running couplings; beyond the Standard Model: neutrino masses, supersymmetry sketch''' .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-particle-physics-and-quantum-field-theory-standard-model> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Standard Model''' ;
  skos:definition '''The gauge field theory SU(3)_C × SU(2)_L × U(1)_Y describing strong, weak, and electromagnetic interactions; all matter fields are quarks and leptons (3 generations each).''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-particle-physics-and-quantum-field-theory> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-particle-physics-and-quantum-field-theory-quark> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''quark''' ;
  skos:definition '''A spin-1/2 fermion carrying color charge (r,g,b) and fractional electric charge; confined in hadrons; 6 flavors: u,d,s,c,b,t.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-particle-physics-and-quantum-field-theory> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-particle-physics-and-quantum-field-theory-lepton> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''lepton''' ;
  skos:definition '''A spin-1/2 fermion without color charge; 6 types: e, μ, τ and their neutrinos ν_e, ν_μ, ν_τ; each carries lepton-family number.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-particle-physics-and-quantum-field-theory> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-particle-physics-and-quantum-field-theory-gauge-boson> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''gauge boson''' ;
  skos:definition '''A spin-1 force-carrying particle arising from local gauge symmetry: photon (U(1)), W^±/Z (SU(2)), gluons g (SU(3)); masses generated by Higgs mechanism except photon and gluon.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-particle-physics-and-quantum-field-theory> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-particle-physics-and-quantum-field-theory-feynman-diagram> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Feynman diagram''' ;
  skos:definition '''A pictorial representation of terms in a perturbative expansion of scattering amplitudes; vertices and propagators encode interaction strengths and particle propagation.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-particle-physics-and-quantum-field-theory> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-particle-physics-and-quantum-field-theory-propagator> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''propagator''' ;
  skos:definition '''The momentum-space Green's function for a quantum field; for a scalar: 1/(p^2 - m^2 + iε); encodes virtual particle exchange between vertices.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-particle-physics-and-quantum-field-theory> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-particle-physics-and-quantum-field-theory-running-coupling> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''running coupling''' ;
  skos:definition '''The effective coupling constant α(μ) that depends on the energy scale μ due to quantum loop corrections (renormalization group); α_s decreases at high energy (asymptotic freedom).''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-particle-physics-and-quantum-field-theory> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-particle-physics-and-quantum-field-theory-spontaneous-symmetry-breaking> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''spontaneous symmetry breaking''' ;
  skos:definition '''A system whose equations are symmetric but whose ground state is not; in the Higgs mechanism, the electroweak SU(2)_L×U(1)_Y symmetry breaks to U(1)_EM, generating W/Z masses.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-particle-physics-and-quantum-field-theory> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-particle-physics-and-quantum-field-theory-higgs-boson> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Higgs boson''' ;
  skos:definition '''The scalar boson (spin-0, m ≈ 125 GeV) arising as the excitation of the Higgs field after spontaneous electroweak symmetry breaking; observed at LHC in 2012.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-particle-physics-and-quantum-field-theory> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-particle-physics-and-quantum-field-theory-color-confinement> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''color confinement''' ;
  skos:definition '''The property of QCD whereby free color-charged particles (quarks, gluons) are never observed; the strong force potential grows with distance, confining quarks inside hadrons.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-particle-physics-and-quantum-field-theory> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-particle-physics-and-quantum-field-theory-asymptotic-freedom> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''asymptotic freedom''' ;
  skos:definition '''The decrease of the QCD coupling α_s at high energies (short distances), allowing perturbative calculations of hard processes; established by Gross, Politzer, and Wilczek (2004 Nobel Prize).''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-particle-physics-and-quantum-field-theory> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-particle-physics-and-quantum-field-theory-cp-violation> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''CP violation''' ;
  skos:definition '''The violation of combined charge-conjugation (C) and parity (P) symmetry; observed in kaon and B-meson systems; necessary (Sakharov conditions) for matter-antimatter asymmetry.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-particle-physics-and-quantum-field-theory> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
