<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-astrophysics-and-cosmology> skos:scopeNote '''stellar structure and evolution; white dwarfs, neutron stars, and black holes; FRW cosmology and Hubble expansion; Big Bang nucleosynthesis; cosmic microwave background; dark matter and dark energy; inflation; gravitational lensing; Chandrasekhar limit; distance ladder and standard candles''' .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-astrophysics-and-cosmology-hubble-s-law> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Hubble's law''' ;
  skos:definition '''Galaxies recede with velocity proportional to distance: v = H_0 * d, where H_0 ≈ 70 km/s/Mpc is the Hubble constant; evidence for an expanding universe.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-astrophysics-and-cosmology> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-astrophysics-and-cosmology-hubble-parameter> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Hubble parameter''' ;
  skos:definition '''H(t) = (da/dt)/a where a(t) is the cosmic scale factor; H_0 is its present value; governs the rate of cosmic expansion.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-astrophysics-and-cosmology> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-astrophysics-and-cosmology-scale-factor> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''scale factor''' ;
  skos:definition '''a(t), a dimensionless function normalised to a(t_0)=1 today; physical distances scale as d_phys = a(t)*d_comoving; its evolution is governed by the Friedmann equations.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-astrophysics-and-cosmology> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-astrophysics-and-cosmology-chandrasekhar-limit> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Chandrasekhar limit''' ;
  skos:definition '''The maximum mass (~1.4 M_sun) of a white dwarf supported by electron degeneracy pressure; exceeded mass collapses to a neutron star or black hole.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-astrophysics-and-cosmology> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-astrophysics-and-cosmology-cosmic-microwave-background> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''cosmic microwave background''' ;
  skos:definition '''The thermal relic radiation from recombination (~380,000 yr after Big Bang) at z ≈ 1100; a near-perfect blackbody at T_0 = 2.725 K with anisotropies ΔT/T ~ 10^{-5} encoding structure formation.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-astrophysics-and-cosmology> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-astrophysics-and-cosmology-dark-matter> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''dark matter''' ;
  skos:definition '''Non-luminous matter constituting ~27% of the cosmic energy budget; inferred from galactic rotation curves, gravitational lensing, and CMB power spectra; particle nature unknown.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-astrophysics-and-cosmology> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-astrophysics-and-cosmology-dark-energy> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''dark energy''' ;
  skos:definition '''An energy component (~68% of cosmic budget) causing accelerated expansion; consistent with a cosmological constant Λ with equation of state w = P/ρ = -1.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-astrophysics-and-cosmology> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-astrophysics-and-cosmology-redshift> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''redshift''' ;
  skos:definition '''The fractional wavelength shift z = (λ_obs - λ_emit)/λ_emit; for cosmological sources, 1+z = 1/a(t_emit), linking observed wavelength to the scale factor at emission.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-astrophysics-and-cosmology> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-astrophysics-and-cosmology-luminosity-distance> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''luminosity distance''' ;
  skos:definition '''d_L = (1+z)*d_comoving; the distance inferred from the observed flux of a standard candle: F = L/(4π d_L^2).''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-astrophysics-and-cosmology> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-astrophysics-and-cosmology-equation-of-state-cosmology> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''equation of state (cosmology)''' ;
  skos:definition '''w = P/ρ characterizing a cosmic fluid: w=0 (matter/dust), w=1/3 (radiation), w=-1 (cosmological constant/dark energy); determines how ρ scales with a.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-astrophysics-and-cosmology> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-astrophysics-and-cosmology-inflation> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''inflation''' ;
  skos:definition '''A period of accelerated exponential expansion in the early universe (t ~ 10^{-36} s) driven by a slow-rolling inflaton field; solves the horizon, flatness, and monopole problems and seeds CMB fluctuations.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-astrophysics-and-cosmology> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-physics-astrophysics-and-cosmology-hubble-s-law> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''Hubble's law''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''v = H_0 * d;  H_0 ≈ 70 km/s/Mpc''' ;
