<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-optics-and-waves> skos:scopeNote '''wave equation and superposition; interference and diffraction; geometric optics: reflection and refraction; Snell's law, total internal reflection; polarization; Fourier analysis and wave packets; Doppler effect; coherence and lasers''' .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-optics-and-waves-constructive-interference> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''constructive interference''' ;
  skos:definition '''Superposition of two waves in phase (path difference = nλ), producing amplitude addition and maximum intensity.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-optics-and-waves> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-optics-and-waves-destructive-interference> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''destructive interference''' ;
  skos:definition '''Superposition of two waves in antiphase (path difference = (n+1/2)λ), producing amplitude cancellation and minimum intensity.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-optics-and-waves> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-optics-and-waves-diffraction> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''diffraction''' ;
  skos:definition '''The bending and spreading of waves around obstacles or through apertures; governed by Huygens' principle and characterized by Fraunhofer or Fresnel regimes.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-optics-and-waves> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-optics-and-waves-snell-s-law> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Snell's law''' ;
  skos:definition '''At an interface between two media, n_1 sin θ_1 = n_2 sin θ_2, relating the angles of incidence and refraction to the indices of refraction.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-optics-and-waves> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-optics-and-waves-index-of-refraction> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''index of refraction''' ;
  skos:definition '''n = c/v_phase; the ratio of the speed of light in vacuum to its phase velocity in the medium; determines refraction angles and optical path length.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-optics-and-waves> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-optics-and-waves-total-internal-reflection> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''total internal reflection''' ;
  skos:definition '''When light in a denser medium strikes an interface at angle greater than θ_c = sin^{-1}(n_2/n_1), it reflects completely back; the basis for optical fibers.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-optics-and-waves> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-optics-and-waves-brewster-s-angle> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Brewster's angle''' ;
  skos:definition '''The angle θ_B = tan^{-1}(n_2/n_1) at which reflected light is completely s-polarized; at this angle the reflected and transmitted beams are perpendicular.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-optics-and-waves> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-optics-and-waves-coherence-length> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''coherence length''' ;
  skos:definition '''The path length difference over which two beams from the same source maintain a fixed phase relationship; inversely proportional to the source's spectral bandwidth.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-optics-and-waves> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-optics-and-waves-group-velocity> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''group velocity''' ;
  skos:definition '''v_g = dω/dk; the velocity at which the envelope of a wave packet and hence energy/information propagates; differs from phase velocity v_φ = ω/k in dispersive media.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-optics-and-waves> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-optics-and-waves-doppler-effect> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Doppler effect''' ;
  skos:definition '''The shift in observed frequency when source and observer are in relative motion: f_obs = f_src*(v_wave ± v_obs)/(v_wave ∓ v_src).''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-optics-and-waves> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-physics-optics-and-waves-wave-equation-1d> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''wave equation (1D)''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''∂^2 y/∂t^2 = v^2 * ∂^2 y/∂x^2''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''equation''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-optics-and-waves> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-physics-optics-and-waves-general-wave-solution> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''general wave solution''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''y(x,t) = A*cos(k*x - omega*t + phi);  v = omega/k''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''equation''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-optics-and-waves> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-physics-optics-and-waves-snell-s-law> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''Snell's law''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''n_1 * sin(theta_1) = n_2 * sin(theta_2)''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''law''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-optics-and-waves> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-physics-optics-and-waves-single-slit-diffraction-minima> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''single-slit diffraction minima''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''a*sin(theta) = m*lambda;  m = ±1, ±2,...''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''equation''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-optics-and-waves> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-physics-optics-and-waves-double-slit-interference-maxima> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''double-slit interference maxima''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''d*sin(theta) = m*lambda;  m = 0, ±1, ±2,...''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''equation''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-optics-and-waves> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-physics-optics-and-waves-thin-film-interference-reflected-n-film-n-air> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''thin-film interference (reflected, n_film > n_air)''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''2*n*t = (m + 1/2)*lambda  (constructive);  2*n*t = m*lambda  (destructive)''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''equation''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-optics-and-waves> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-physics-optics-and-waves-group-velocity> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''group velocity''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''v_g = domega/dk''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''equation''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-optics-and-waves> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-physics-optics-and-waves-rayleigh-criterion-resolution> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''Rayleigh criterion (resolution)''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''theta_min = 1.22 * lambda / D''' ;
