<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-nuclear-and-atomic-physics> a kcc:Topic ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Nuclear and Atomic Physics''' ;
  kcc:level '''undergrad''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#domain-physics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-nuclear-and-atomic-physics> skos:scopeNote '''Rutherford scattering and the nuclear model; radioactive decay: alpha, beta, gamma; nuclear binding energy and the semi-empirical mass formula; nuclear reactions and Q-value; fission and fusion; atomic spectra and selection rules; Zeeman and Stark effects; spin-orbit coupling and fine structure; hyperfine structure''' .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-nuclear-and-atomic-physics-binding-energy> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''binding energy''' ;
  skos:definition '''The energy required to disassemble a nucleus into its constituent protons and neutrons: B = (Z*m_p + N*m_n - M_nucleus)*c^2.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-nuclear-and-atomic-physics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-nuclear-and-atomic-physics-mass-defect> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''mass defect''' ;
  skos:definition '''The difference between the total mass of individual nucleons and the actual nuclear mass: Δm = Z*m_p + N*m_n - M; equals B/c^2.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-nuclear-and-atomic-physics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-nuclear-and-atomic-physics-radioactive-decay-law> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''radioactive decay law''' ;
  skos:definition '''The number of undecayed nuclei decreases exponentially: N(t) = N_0 exp(-λt), where λ is the decay constant; half-life t_{1/2} = ln2/λ.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-nuclear-and-atomic-physics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-nuclear-and-atomic-physics-alpha-decay> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''alpha decay''' ;
  skos:definition '''Emission of a ^4He nucleus; governed by quantum tunneling through the Coulomb barrier; described by the Geiger-Nuttall law.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-nuclear-and-atomic-physics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-nuclear-and-atomic-physics-beta-decay> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''beta decay (β^-)''' ;
  skos:definition '''Conversion of a neutron to a proton with emission of an electron and anti-electron-neutrino: n → p + e^- + ν̄_e; mediated by the weak force.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-nuclear-and-atomic-physics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-nuclear-and-atomic-physics-q-value> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Q-value''' ;
  skos:definition '''Q = (m_reactants - m_products)*c^2; the energy released (Q > 0, exothermic) or absorbed (Q < 0, endothermic) in a nuclear reaction.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-nuclear-and-atomic-physics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-nuclear-and-atomic-physics-fine-structure> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''fine structure''' ;
  skos:definition '''Small splitting of atomic energy levels due to spin-orbit coupling (L·S interaction), relativistic corrections, and the Darwin term; of order α^2 E_n.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-nuclear-and-atomic-physics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
