<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-physics-nuclear-and-atomic-physics-rutherford-scattering-cross-section> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''Rutherford scattering cross section''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''d sigma/d Omega = (Z_1*Z_2*e^2/(4*E))^2 * 1/sin^4(theta/2)''' ;
