<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-physics-nuclear-and-atomic-physics-magnetic-moment-orbital> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''magnetic moment (orbital)''' ;
