<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-plasma-physics-and-fluid-dynamics-plasma> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''plasma''' ;
  skos:definition '''A quasi-neutral ionized gas in which collective electromagnetic effects dominate; the fourth state of matter, comprising most of the visible universe.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-plasma-physics-and-fluid-dynamics> ;
