<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-plasma-physics-and-fluid-dynamics-vlasov-equation> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Vlasov equation''' ;
  skos:definition '''The collisionless Boltzmann equation ∂f/∂t + v·∇f + (q/m)(E+v×B)·∂f/∂v = 0 governing the distribution function f(r,v,t) of a plasma.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-plasma-physics-and-fluid-dynamics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-plasma-physics-and-fluid-dynamics-reynolds-number> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Reynolds number''' ;
  skos:definition '''Re = ρvL/μ; the ratio of inertial to viscous forces; low Re → laminar flow; high Re → turbulent flow; transition typically Re ~ 10^3–10^4.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-plasma-physics-and-fluid-dynamics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-physics-plasma-physics-and-fluid-dynamics-navier-stokes-equation> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Navier-Stokes equation''' ;
  skos:definition '''ρ(∂v/∂t + v·∇v) = -∇P + μ∇^2v + f; governs the velocity field of a viscous incompressible Newtonian fluid.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-physics-plasma-physics-and-fluid-dynamics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
