<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-gases-and-kinetic-molecular-theory> skos:scopeNote '''Ideal gas law and standard conditions; Partial pressures (Dalton's law); Gas stoichiometry and molar volume; Effusion and diffusion (Graham's law); Kinetic-molecular theory postulates; Maxwell-Boltzmann speed distribution; Real gases: van der Waals equation; Compressibility factor Z''' .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-gases-and-kinetic-molecular-theory-ideal-gas> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''ideal gas''' ;
  skos:definition '''A hypothetical gas whose particles have no intermolecular forces and negligible volume, obeying PV = nRT exactly.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-gases-and-kinetic-molecular-theory> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
