<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-chemistry-gases-and-kinetic-molecular-theory-dalton-s-law-of-partial-pressures> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''Dalton's law of partial pressures''' ;
