<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-thermodynamics> skos:scopeNote '''First law: internal energy, heat, and work; Enthalpy and Hess's law; Standard enthalpies of formation and combustion; Entropy and the second and third laws; Gibbs free energy and spontaneity; Relationship between delta-G and the equilibrium constant; Temperature dependence of equilibrium (van't Hoff equation); Maxwell relations and thermodynamic identities; Helmholtz free energy; Chemical potential and partial molar quantities''' .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-thermodynamics-internal-energy-u> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''internal energy (U)''' ;
  skos:definition '''The total microscopic energy of a system; changes by dU = q + w (heat added plus work done on the system).''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-thermodynamics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-thermodynamics-enthalpy-h> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''enthalpy (H)''' ;
  skos:definition '''A state function defined as H = U + PV; at constant pressure, delta-H equals heat transferred.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-thermodynamics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-thermodynamics-entropy-s> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''entropy (S)''' ;
  skos:definition '''A state function measuring the dispersal of energy; for a reversible process dS = dq_rev / T.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-thermodynamics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-thermodynamics-gibbs-free-energy-g> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Gibbs free energy (G)''' ;
  skos:definition '''G = H - TS; a decrease in G at constant T and P indicates a spontaneous process.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-thermodynamics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-thermodynamics-helmholtz-free-energy-a> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Helmholtz free energy (A)''' ;
  skos:definition '''A = U - TS; a decrease in A at constant T and V indicates spontaneity; equal to reversible work.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-thermodynamics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-thermodynamics-standard-state> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''standard state''' ;
  skos:definition '''A reference condition: pure substance at 1 bar (solutes at 1 mol/L activity), specified temperature (usually 298.15 K).''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-thermodynamics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-thermodynamics-hess-s-law> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Hess's law''' ;
  skos:definition '''The enthalpy change of a reaction equals the algebraic sum of enthalpies of any sequence of steps connecting reactants to products.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-thermodynamics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-thermodynamics-heat-capacity-c> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''heat capacity (C)''' ;
  skos:definition '''The amount of heat required to raise the temperature of a substance by one kelvin; C_P = (dH/dT)_P, C_V = (dU/dT)_V.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-thermodynamics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-thermodynamics-chemical-potential-mu> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''chemical potential (mu)''' ;
  skos:definition '''The partial molar Gibbs free energy of a species; mu_i = (dG/dn_i)_{T,P,n_j}.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-thermodynamics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-thermodynamics-third-law-of-thermodynamics> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''third law of thermodynamics''' ;
  skos:definition '''The entropy of a perfect crystalline substance is zero at absolute zero temperature (0 K).''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-thermodynamics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-thermodynamics-van-t-hoff-enthalpy> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''van't Hoff enthalpy''' ;
  skos:definition '''The enthalpy change of a process derived from the temperature dependence of the equilibrium constant via d(ln K)/d(1/T) = -delta_H/R.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-thermodynamics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-thermodynamics-kirchhoff-s-law> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Kirchhoff's law''' ;
  skos:definition '''The temperature dependence of reaction enthalpy: d(delta_H)/dT = delta_C_P.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-thermodynamics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-chemistry-thermodynamics-first-law-of-thermodynamics> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''First law of thermodynamics''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''dU = q + w  (or dU = delta_q - P_ext dV for PV work)''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''law''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-thermodynamics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-chemistry-thermodynamics-enthalpy-definition> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Enthalpy definition''' ;
  skos:definition '''H = U + PV  =>  dH = dU + P dV + V dP  =>  dH_P = q_P''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-thermodynamics> ;
  kcc:canonType '''definition''' ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-chemistry-thermodynamics-second-law-clausius-inequality> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''Second law (Clausius inequality)''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''dS >= dq / T  (equality for reversible)''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''law''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-thermodynamics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-chemistry-thermodynamics-gibbs-free-energy> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Gibbs free energy''' ;
  skos:definition '''G = H - T*S  =>  dG = V dP - S dT''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-thermodynamics> ;
  kcc:canonType '''definition''' ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-chemistry-thermodynamics-spontaneity-criterion-constant-t-p> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''Spontaneity criterion (constant T, P)''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''delta_G < 0 (spontaneous), = 0 (equilibrium), > 0 (non-spontaneous)''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''law''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-thermodynamics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-chemistry-thermodynamics-standard-free-energy-and-equilibrium-constant> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''Standard free energy and equilibrium constant''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''delta_G^o = -R*T*ln(K)''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''equation''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-thermodynamics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-chemistry-thermodynamics-gibbs-helmholtz-equation> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''Gibbs-Helmholtz equation''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''d(G/T)/d(1/T) = H''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''equation''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-thermodynamics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-chemistry-thermodynamics-van-t-hoff-equation> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''van't Hoff equation''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''d(ln K)/d(1/T) = -delta_H^o / R''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''equation''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-thermodynamics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-chemistry-thermodynamics-entropy-change-for-reversible-process> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''Entropy change for reversible process''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''delta_S = integral(dq_rev / T)''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''equation''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-thermodynamics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-chemistry-thermodynamics-fundamental-thermodynamic-relation> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''Fundamental thermodynamic relation''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''dU = T dS - P dV + sum(mu_i dn_i)''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''equation''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-thermodynamics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-chemistry-thermodynamics-maxwell-relation-from-g> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''Maxwell relation (from G)''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''(dS/dP)_T = -(dV/dT)_P''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''equation''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-thermodynamics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-chemistry-thermodynamics-kirchhoff-s-law> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''Kirchhoff's law''' ;
