<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-chemical-equilibrium-heterogeneous-equilibrium> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''heterogeneous equilibrium''' ;
  skos:definition '''An equilibrium involving reactants or products in more than one phase; pure solids and liquids are omitted from the K expression.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-chemical-equilibrium> ;
