<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-chemical-kinetics-elementary-step> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''elementary step''' ;
  skos:definition '''A single molecular event in a mechanism; its molecularity equals the order of that step.''' ;
