<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-chemical-kinetics-rate-determining-step> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''rate-determining step''' ;
  skos:definition '''The slowest step in a reaction mechanism, which limits the overall reaction rate.''' ;
