<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-chemistry-atomic-structure-and-quantum-chemistry-schrodinger-equation-time-independent> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''Schrodinger equation (time-independent)''' ;
