<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-chemical-bonding-and-molecular-structure> skos:scopeNote '''Ionic, covalent, and metallic bonding; Lewis structures, formal charges, and resonance; VSEPR theory and molecular geometry; Polarity and dipole moments; Valence bond theory (hybridization: sp, sp2, sp3, sp3d, sp3d2); Molecular orbital (MO) theory: bonding/antibonding MOs, bond order; MO diagrams for homodiatomic molecules (H2 through Ne2); Intermolecular forces: London dispersion, dipole-dipole, hydrogen bonding; Lattice energy and Born-Haber cycle; Band theory of solids''' .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-chemical-bonding-and-molecular-structure-bond-order> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''bond order''' ;
