<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-chemical-bonding-and-molecular-structure-hydrogen-bond> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''hydrogen bond''' ;
  skos:definition '''A strong electrostatic interaction between a hydrogen atom covalently bonded to a highly electronegative atom (N, O, F) and a lone pair on another such atom.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-chemical-bonding-and-molecular-structure> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
