<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-chemical-bonding-and-molecular-structure-lattice-energy> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''lattice energy''' ;
  skos:definition '''The energy released when gaseous ions come together to form an ionic crystal; related to ionic charges and radii via the Born-Lande equation.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-chemical-bonding-and-molecular-structure> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-chemical-bonding-and-molecular-structure-formal-charge> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''formal charge''' ;
  skos:definition '''A bookkeeping charge assigned to an atom in a Lewis structure: formal charge = (valence electrons) - (lone-pair electrons) - 0.5*(bonding electrons).''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-chemical-bonding-and-molecular-structure> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-chemical-bonding-and-molecular-structure-resonance> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''resonance''' ;
  skos:definition '''The description of a molecule or ion as a hybrid of two or more Lewis structures (resonance structures) that differ only in electron placement.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-chemical-bonding-and-molecular-structure> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-chemical-bonding-and-molecular-structure-electronegativity> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''electronegativity''' ;
  skos:definition '''A measure of an atom's ability to attract bonding electrons to itself; increases across a period and decreases down a group (Pauling scale).''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-chemical-bonding-and-molecular-structure> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
