<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-organic-reactions-and-mechanisms> skos:scopeNote '''Functional groups and IUPAC nomenclature; Stereochemistry: chirality, R/S, E/Z, diastereomers, meso compounds; Nucleophilic substitution: SN1 and SN2; Elimination reactions: E1 and E2; Zaitsev's rule; Electrophilic addition to alkenes; Markovnikov's rule; Electrophilic aromatic substitution (EAS): nitration, halogenation, Friedel-Crafts; Nucleophilic addition to carbonyls (aldehydes, ketones, carboxylic acid derivatives); Reactions of carboxylic acids and derivatives (esterification, saponification, amide formation); Aldol condensation and Claisen condensation; Oxidation and reduction of organic functional groups; Pericyclic reactions: Diels-Alder, electrocyclic (Woodward-Hoffmann rules)''' .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-organic-reactions-and-mechanisms-nucleophile> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''nucleophile''' ;
