  skos:prefLabel '''18-electron rule''' ;
  skos:definition '''Stable transition-metal organometallic compounds tend to have 18 electrons in the metal valence shell (filled bonding MOs).''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-coordination-chemistry-and-inorganic-chemistry> ;
