  skos:prefLabel '''oxidative addition''' ;
  skos:definition '''A reaction in which a metal inserts into a bond (X-Y), increasing the metal's oxidation state by 2 and coordination number by 2.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-coordination-chemistry-and-inorganic-chemistry> ;
