<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-chemistry-statistical-thermodynamics-and-partition-functions-equipartition-mean-energy-per-quadratic-mode> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''Equipartition (mean energy per quadratic mode)''' ;
