<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-quantum-chemistry> skos:scopeNote '''Variational principle and the variational theorem; Perturbation theory (first and second order); Born-Oppenheimer approximation; Hartree-Fock method and self-consistent field (SCF) theory; Basis sets (STO, STO-3G, 6-31G, correlation-consistent cc-pVXZ); Electron correlation: configuration interaction (CI), MP2, coupled cluster (CCSD(T)); Density functional theory (DFT): Hohenberg-Kohn theorems, Kohn-Sham equations; Spin states and spin-orbit coupling; Molecular orbital symmetry and group theory in quantum chemistry; Potential energy surfaces and transition-state structure''' .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-quantum-chemistry-born-oppenheimer-approximation> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Born-Oppenheimer approximation''' ;
  skos:definition '''The assumption that electrons adjust instantaneously to nuclear positions because electrons are much lighter; separates nuclear and electronic wavefunctions.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-quantum-chemistry> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-quantum-chemistry-variational-principle> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''variational principle''' ;
  skos:definition '''The expectation value of the Hamiltonian for any trial wavefunction is greater than or equal to the true ground-state energy: <psi|H|psi> >= E_0.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-quantum-chemistry> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-quantum-chemistry-hartree-fock-hf-method> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Hartree-Fock (HF) method''' ;
  skos:definition '''A mean-field SCF method that approximates the many-electron wavefunction as a single Slater determinant of spin-orbitals; neglects electron correlation.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-quantum-chemistry> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-quantum-chemistry-basis-set> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''basis set''' ;
  skos:definition '''A finite set of mathematical functions (atomic orbitals) used to expand molecular orbitals in quantum chemistry calculations.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-quantum-chemistry> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-quantum-chemistry-electron-correlation-energy> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''electron correlation energy''' ;
  skos:definition '''The difference between the exact non-relativistic energy and the Hartree-Fock energy: E_corr = E_exact - E_HF; always negative.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-quantum-chemistry> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-quantum-chemistry-density-functional-theory-dft> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''density functional theory (DFT)''' ;
  skos:definition '''A method that replaces the many-electron wavefunction with the electron density rho(r) as the fundamental variable, based on the Hohenberg-Kohn theorems.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-quantum-chemistry> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-quantum-chemistry-exchange-correlation-functional> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''exchange-correlation functional''' ;
  skos:definition '''The unknown functional E_xc[rho] in DFT that accounts for exchange (Pauli) and correlation effects; approximated by LDA, GGA, hybrid functionals.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-quantum-chemistry> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-quantum-chemistry-coupled-cluster-cc-theory> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''coupled cluster (CC) theory''' ;
  skos:definition '''A high-accuracy post-HF method that expresses the wavefunction as exp(T)|HF>; CCSD(T) is considered the 'gold standard' for molecular energetics.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-quantum-chemistry> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-quantum-chemistry-slater-determinant> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Slater determinant''' ;
  skos:definition '''An antisymmetrized product of spin-orbitals that automatically satisfies the Pauli exclusion principle for fermions.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-quantum-chemistry> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-quantum-chemistry-potential-energy-surface-pes> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''potential energy surface (PES)''' ;
  skos:definition '''The electronic energy as a function of nuclear coordinates; stationary points correspond to equilibrium geometries and transition states.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-quantum-chemistry> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-chemistry-quantum-chemistry-variational-theorem> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''Variational theorem''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''E_trial = <psi_trial|H|psi_trial> / <psi_trial|psi_trial> >= E_0''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''law''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-quantum-chemistry> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-chemistry-quantum-chemistry-first-order-perturbation-energy-correction> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''First-order perturbation energy correction''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''E_n^(1) = <psi_n^(0)|H'|psi_n^(0)>''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''equation''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-quantum-chemistry> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-chemistry-quantum-chemistry-second-order-perturbation-energy-correction> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''Second-order perturbation energy correction''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''E_n^(2) = sum_{m != n} |<psi_m^(0)|H'|psi_n^(0)>|^2 / (E_n^(0) - E_m^(0))''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''equation''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-quantum-chemistry> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-chemistry-quantum-chemistry-hohenberg-kohn-theorem-i> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''Hohenberg-Kohn theorem I''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''The external potential V_ext(r) is determined uniquely (up to a constant) by the ground-state electron density rho(r).''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''law''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-quantum-chemistry> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-chemistry-quantum-chemistry-kohn-sham-equations> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''Kohn-Sham equations''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''[-hbar^2/(2m) nabla^2 + V_KS(r)] phi_i(r) = epsilon_i phi_i(r)  where V_KS = V_ext + V_Hartree + V_xc''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''equation''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-quantum-chemistry> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-chemistry-quantum-chemistry-hf-energy-expression> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''HF energy expression''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''E_HF = sum_i h_ii + (1/2) sum_{ij} (J_ij - K_ij)''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''equation''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-quantum-chemistry> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-chemistry-quantum-chemistry-coupled-cluster-wavefunction-ansatz> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Coupled cluster wavefunction ansatz''' ;
  skos:definition '''|CC> = exp(T)|HF>  where T = T_1 + T_2 + ... (cluster operator)''' ;
