<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-chemistry-biochemistry-fundamentals-glycolysis-net-reaction> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''Glycolysis net reaction''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''Glucose + 2 NAD+ + 2 ADP + 2 Pi -> 2 Pyruvate + 2 NADH + 2 ATP + 2 H2O''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''equation''' ;
