<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-analytical-chemistry-and-solution-equilibria> skos:scopeNote '''Activity coefficients and Debye-Huckel theory; Complexometric titrations (EDTA); conditional formation constants; Precipitation titrations; Fajans and Mohr methods; Potentiometry: ion-selective electrodes, glass electrode, pH measurement; Voltammetry and polarography; Chromatography: plate theory, resolution, van Deemter equation; Statistical treatment of analytical data: mean, standard deviation, confidence intervals; Propagation of error and significant figures; Calibration methods: external standard, standard addition, internal standard''' .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-analytical-chemistry-and-solution-equilibria-activity-a> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''activity (a)''' ;
  skos:definition '''The effective concentration of a species accounting for non-ideal interactions: a_i = gamma_i * [i] / c^o (c^o = 1 M standard).''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-analytical-chemistry-and-solution-equilibria> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-analytical-chemistry-and-solution-equilibria-activity-coefficient-gamma> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''activity coefficient (gamma)''' ;
  skos:definition '''A dimensionless factor relating activity to molarity; approaches 1 at infinite dilution; decreases with increasing ionic strength.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-analytical-chemistry-and-solution-equilibria> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-analytical-chemistry-and-solution-equilibria-ionic-strength-i> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''ionic strength (I)''' ;
  skos:definition '''A measure of the total ion concentration in solution: I = (1/2) * sum(c_i * z_i^2) for all ions i.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-analytical-chemistry-and-solution-equilibria> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-analytical-chemistry-and-solution-equilibria-debye-huckel-limiting-law> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Debye-Huckel limiting law''' ;
  skos:definition '''log(gamma) = -A * z^2 * sqrt(I) for dilute solutions; A = 0.509 in water at 25 degrees C.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-analytical-chemistry-and-solution-equilibria> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-analytical-chemistry-and-solution-equilibria-conditional-formation-constant-k-f> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''conditional formation constant (K_f')''' ;
  skos:definition '''An effective formation constant for a metal-EDTA complex at a specified pH, corrected for competing protonation equilibria of EDTA: K_f' = alpha_Y4- * K_f.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-analytical-chemistry-and-solution-equilibria> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-analytical-chemistry-and-solution-equilibria-theoretical-plate-n> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''theoretical plate (N)''' ;
  skos:definition '''A measure of chromatographic column efficiency: N = (t_R / sigma)^2 or N = 16(t_R/W)^2.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-analytical-chemistry-and-solution-equilibria> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-analytical-chemistry-and-solution-equilibria-resolution-r-s> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''resolution (R_s)''' ;
  skos:definition '''A measure of chromatographic separation: R_s = 2(t_R2 - t_R1) / (W_1 + W_2); R_s >= 1.5 for baseline resolution.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-analytical-chemistry-and-solution-equilibria> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-analytical-chemistry-and-solution-equilibria-van-deemter-equation> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''van Deemter equation''' ;
  skos:definition '''H = A + B/u + C*u, where H is the height equivalent to a theoretical plate, u is the mobile-phase velocity, A=eddy diffusion, B=longitudinal diffusion, C=mass transfer.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-analytical-chemistry-and-solution-equilibria> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-analytical-chemistry-and-solution-equilibria-standard-addition-method> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''standard addition method''' ;
  skos:definition '''A calibration technique for complex matrices in which known amounts of analyte are added to the sample solution to correct for matrix effects.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-analytical-chemistry-and-solution-equilibria> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-chemistry-analytical-chemistry-and-solution-equilibria-propagation-of-uncertainty> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''propagation of uncertainty''' ;
  skos:definition '''The method for calculating the uncertainty in a result derived from uncertain measurements; for sums/differences, absolute uncertainties add in quadrature; for products/quotients, relative uncertainties add in quadrature.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-analytical-chemistry-and-solution-equilibria> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-chemistry-analytical-chemistry-and-solution-equilibria-debye-huckel-limiting-law> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''Debye-Huckel limiting law''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''log(gamma_i) = -A * z_i^2 * sqrt(I)  (A = 0.509 at 25 degrees C in H2O)''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''equation''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-chemistry-analytical-chemistry-and-solution-equilibria> ;
