<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-mathematics-algebra-and-polynomial-theory-rational-root-theorem> a math:Equation ;
  rdfs:label '''Rational root theorem''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''If p/q is a rational root of a_n x^n + ... + a_0 (in lowest terms), then p | a_0 and q | a_n.''' ;
