  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-mathematics-precalculus-and-functions-standard-conic-forms> a math:Equation ;
  rdfs:label '''Standard conic forms''' ;
