<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression> skos:scopeNote '''Simple and multiple linear regression; OLS estimation and properties; Gauss-Markov theorem and BLUE; Measures of fit: R², adjusted R²; Hypothesis testing: t-test and F-test; Confidence intervals; Omitted variable bias; Multicollinearity; Heteroskedasticity and GLS; Serial correlation and Newey-West standard errors; Functional form: logs, quadratics, interactions''' .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression-ols-ordinary-least-squares> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''OLS (Ordinary Least Squares)''' ;
  skos:definition '''A method of estimating regression coefficients by minimizing the sum of squared residuals.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression-regression-coefficient> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''regression coefficient (β)''' ;
  skos:definition '''The estimated change in the dependent variable associated with a one-unit increase in an independent variable, holding other variables constant.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression-residual> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''residual''' ;
  skos:definition '''The difference between the observed and fitted value of the dependent variable: e_i = y_i - ŷ_i.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression-r-coefficient-of-determination> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''R² (coefficient of determination)''' ;
  skos:definition '''The proportion of variance in the dependent variable explained by the regression: R² = 1 - SSR/SST; ranges from 0 to 1.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression-adjusted-r> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''adjusted R²''' ;
  skos:definition '''R² adjusted for the number of regressors: R̄² = 1 - [(1-R²)(n-1)/(n-k-1)]; penalizes for additional variables.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression-t-statistic> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''t-statistic''' ;
  skos:definition '''The ratio of an estimated coefficient to its standard error: t = β̂/SE(β̂); used to test whether a coefficient is statistically different from a hypothesized value.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression-f-statistic> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''F-statistic''' ;
  skos:definition '''A test statistic for the joint significance of multiple coefficients; tests whether all slope coefficients are simultaneously zero.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression-p-value> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''p-value''' ;
  skos:definition '''The probability of observing a test statistic at least as extreme as the one calculated, under the null hypothesis; a small p-value (< 0.05) rejects the null.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression-omitted-variable-bias> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''omitted variable bias''' ;
  skos:definition '''Bias in OLS estimates when a variable that affects the dependent variable and is correlated with included regressors is excluded from the regression.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression-heteroskedasticity> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''heteroskedasticity''' ;
  skos:definition '''A violation of OLS assumption in which the variance of the error term varies across observations; OLS remains unbiased but is no longer efficient, and standard errors are incorrect.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression-multicollinearity> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''multicollinearity''' ;
  skos:definition '''A condition in which two or more independent variables are highly correlated, making it difficult to estimate their individual coefficients precisely.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression-gauss-markov-theorem> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Gauss-Markov theorem''' ;
  skos:definition '''Under classical OLS assumptions (linearity, exogeneity, homoskedasticity, no serial correlation), OLS is BLUE: Best Linear Unbiased Estimator.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression-standard-error> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''standard error''' ;
  skos:definition '''The estimated standard deviation of an estimator; measures the precision of the coefficient estimate.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression-ols-estimator-simple-regression> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''OLS estimator (simple regression)''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''β̂_1 = Σ(x_i - x̄)(y_i - ȳ) / Σ(x_i - x̄)²  =  Cov(x,y)/Var(x)''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''equation''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression-ols-estimator-matrix-form> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''OLS estimator (matrix form)''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''β̂ = (X'X)^{-1} X'y''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''equation''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression-decomposition-of-variance> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''Decomposition of variance''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''SST = SSE + SSR;  R² = SSE/SST = 1 - SSR/SST''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''equation''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression-t-test-for-a-coefficient> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''t-test for a coefficient''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''H_0: β_k = 0;  t = β̂_k / SE(β̂_k) ~ t_{n-k-1} under H_0''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''equation''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression-confidence-interval-for-coefficient> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''Confidence interval for coefficient''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''[β̂ - t_{α/2} · SE(β̂),  β̂ + t_{α/2} · SE(β̂)]''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''equation''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression-f-test-for-joint-significance> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''F-test for joint significance''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''F = [(SSR_R - SSR_U)/q] / [SSR_U/(n-k-1)] ~ F_{q, n-k-1}''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''equation''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression-omitted-variable-bias-formula> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''Omitted variable bias formula''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''plim(β̂_1) = β_1 + β_2·δ_{21}; where δ_{21} = Cov(x_2,x_1)/Var(x_1) (from auxiliary regression x_2 on x_1)''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''equation''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression-gauss-markov-theorem> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''Gauss-Markov theorem''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''Under assumptions: (1) linearity, (2) random sampling, (3) no perfect collinearity, (4) E[u|X]=0, (5) homoskedasticity; OLS is BLUE.''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''principle''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression-white-s-heteroskedasticity-consistent-se> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''White's heteroskedasticity-consistent SE''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''Use robust standard errors: V̂(β̂) = (X'X)^{-1}(Σ ê_i²·x_i·x_i')(X'X)^{-1} when Var(u_i|x_i) ≠ σ².''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''equation''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression-log-log-interpretation> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''Log-log interpretation''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''ln(y) = β_0 + β_1·ln(x): β_1 is the elasticity of y with respect to x.''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''principle''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression-log-linear-interpretation> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''Log-linear interpretation''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''ln(y) = β_0 + β_1·x: β_1 × 100 is the approximate % change in y per unit change in x.''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''principle''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-ols-and-regression> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods> a kcc:Topic ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Econometrics: Causal Inference and Advanced Methods''' ;
  kcc:level '''graduate''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#domain-economics> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods> skos:scopeNote '''Endogeneity and sources of bias; Instrumental variables (IV) and 2SLS; Randomized controlled trials (RCTs); Difference-in-differences (DiD); Regression discontinuity design (RDD); Panel data: fixed effects and random effects; Hausman test; Simultaneous equations and identification; Weak instruments and the first-stage F-test; Local average treatment effect (LATE)''' .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods-endogeneity> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''endogeneity''' ;
  skos:definition '''A condition in which a regressor is correlated with the error term, causing OLS to be biased and inconsistent; arises from omitted variables, reverse causality, or measurement error.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods-instrumental-variable-iv> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''instrumental variable (IV)''' ;
  skos:definition '''A variable that is correlated with an endogenous regressor (relevance) but uncorrelated with the error term (exclusion restriction); used to obtain consistent estimates.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods-2sls-two-stage-least-squares> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''2SLS (two-stage least squares)''' ;
  skos:definition '''An IV estimation procedure: first regress the endogenous variable on instruments and exogenous controls; then use fitted values in the second-stage regression.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods-exclusion-restriction> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''exclusion restriction''' ;
  skos:definition '''The identifying assumption that an instrument affects the outcome only through the endogenous variable of interest, not directly.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods-difference-in-differences-did> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''difference-in-differences (DiD)''' ;
  skos:definition '''A quasi-experimental method comparing changes in outcomes over time between a treatment group and a control group to identify causal effects.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods-regression-discontinuity-rdd> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''regression discontinuity (RDD)''' ;
  skos:definition '''An identification strategy exploiting a known discontinuity in treatment assignment at a threshold of a running variable.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods-fixed-effects-fe> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''fixed effects (FE)''' ;
  skos:definition '''A panel data estimator that removes time-invariant unobserved heterogeneity by demeaning within each unit.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods-random-effects-re> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''random effects (RE)''' ;
  skos:definition '''A panel data estimator that treats the unit-level unobserved effects as random and uncorrelated with regressors; more efficient than FE if the assumption holds.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods-hausman-test> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''Hausman test''' ;
  skos:definition '''A specification test comparing FE and RE estimates; a significant difference indicates correlation between unobserved effects and regressors, favoring FE.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods-late-local-average-treatment-effect> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''LATE (Local Average Treatment Effect)''' ;
  skos:definition '''The average treatment effect for compliers — units whose treatment status is changed by the instrument; the IV estimand under heterogeneous treatment effects.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods-complier> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''complier''' ;
  skos:definition '''An individual whose treatment status changes in the same direction as the instrument; IV identifies the treatment effect for compliers only.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods-weak-instruments> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''weak instruments''' ;
  skos:definition '''Instruments with low correlation with the endogenous variable, leading to biased IV estimates and invalid inference; diagnosed by first-stage F-statistic (rule of thumb: F > 10).''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#term-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods-parallel-trends-assumption> a kcc:GlossaryTerm ;
  skos:prefLabel '''parallel trends assumption''' ;
  skos:definition '''The identifying assumption for DiD: absent the treatment, the treated and control groups would have followed the same trend in outcomes.''' ;
  skos:broader <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext ;
  skos:inScheme kcc:CanonScheme .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods-iv-estimator-just-identified> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''IV estimator (just-identified)''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''β̂_IV = (Z'X)^{-1}Z'y  =  Cov(Z,Y)/Cov(Z,X)''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''equation''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods-2sls-procedure> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''2SLS procedure''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''Stage 1: X̂ = Z(Z'Z)^{-1}Z'X;  Stage 2: β̂_2SLS = (X̂'X)^{-1}X̂'y''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''equation''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods-iv-consistency-condition> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''IV consistency condition''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''Cov(Z, u) = 0 (exclusion) and Cov(Z, X) ≠ 0 (relevance)''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''principle''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods-did-estimator> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''DiD estimator''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''β_DiD = (Ȳ_{treat,post} - Ȳ_{treat,pre}) - (Ȳ_{control,post} - Ȳ_{control,pre})''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''equation''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods-did-regression-form> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''DiD regression form''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''Y_{it} = α + β·Treat_i + γ·Post_t + δ·(Treat_i × Post_t) + ε_{it};  δ = DiD estimate''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''equation''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods-sharp-rdd-estimand> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''Sharp RDD estimand''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''τ_RDD = lim_{x→c+} E[Y|X=x] - lim_{x→c-} E[Y|X=x];  discontinuity in E[Y|X] at cutoff c''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''equation''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods-fixed-effects-estimator-within> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''Fixed effects estimator (within)''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''β̂_FE = (X̃'X̃)^{-1}X̃'Ỹ  where X̃_{it} = X_{it} - X̄_i (within-group demeaning)''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''equation''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods-hausman-test-statistic> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''Hausman test statistic''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''H = (β̂_FE - β̂_RE)'[Var(β̂_FE) - Var(β̂_RE)]^{-1}(β̂_FE - β̂_RE) ~ χ²_k under H_0 (RE consistent)''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''equation''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods-late-theorem-imbens-angrist> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''LATE theorem (Imbens-Angrist)''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''IV estimand = E[Y_1 - Y_0 | complier] = LATE; identifies effect only for those whose treatment is changed by the instrument.''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''principle''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods-weak-instrument-rule-of-thumb> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''Weak instrument rule of thumb''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''First-stage F-statistic > 10 (Staiger-Stock); or use Stock-Yogo critical values for size distortion.''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''principle''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .
<https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#formula-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods-wald-estimator-binary-instrument> a kcc:Formula ;
  rdfs:label '''Wald estimator (binary instrument)''' ;
  math:hasStatement '''β̂_IV = [E(Y|Z=1) - E(Y|Z=0)] / [E(X|Z=1) - E(X|Z=0)]''' ;
  kcc:canonType '''equation''' ;
  dct:subject <https://socioprophet.github.io/ontogenesis/domains/knowledge-commons-canon#topic-economics-econometrics-causal-inference-and-advanced-methods> ;
  kcc:inKnowledgeContext kcc:CanonKnowledgeContext .

